 class=m><span class=title> Taking advantage of the lazy, role playing a rogue and makin</span><hr size=1> As a 20th level, completely non-twinked rogue, I still don't have a great deal of cash.  This is how I parlayed 50pp into something much better. <BR>  <BR> I was travelling in Greater Faydark to sell some very low level booty, raw-hide pieces, lightstones, words, etc.  I still try to sell anything that I ca get at least 1pp from players, rather than get raped at a merchant. <BR>  <BR> While I was doing this, I spotted a guy selling Elf Hide Gloves for 50pp.  Well, I know these can sell for much more, so I buy them.  Later, as I moved from zone to zone selling my loot, I advertised them for 90pp.  Well, this same guy sees this and harrasses me for charging too much, and that I should just give them away for 50  or less.  Of course he does this publically, ruining any chance of a sale. I broadcast publically that I'll buy everyone he has at that price, because it is so low.  He agrees.  I have no more cash yet, so I hold off. <BR>  <BR> Later, in another zone, I get a buyer immediately upon advertising.   I then contact the original seller, and buy two more.  These sell in the same night, one for 90pp the other in trade for a shield of the slain unicorn. <BR>  <BR> The next day, I trade the shield for a fire emerald necklace, which I immediately trade for a serpentine bracer. <BR>  <BR> So, a poor rogue (50pp at level 20) parlays that 50pp into serpentine bracers. <BR>  <BR> Lets see that lazy twinker acomplish that.  Of course, he doesn't need to since he takes the non-roleplaying, easy way out, basically cheating.  <BR>  <BR>  He probably plays monopoly and takes money from the bank too, instead of doing that stupid buy and build on property thing.... <p>Noudess Icescout - Halas - Rodcet Nife
<BR>
Vikings?  You have got to be kidding.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub2.ezboard.com/uhalen.showPublicProfile>Halen</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Global user</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/15/00 10:19:49 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Taking advantage of the lazy, role playing a rogue and m</span><hr size=1> I can do better :-) <BR>  <BR> Crude steins - pick them up for nothing from Bouncer corpses in Oggok, run to South Karana, sell for 60pp. Repeat until wealthy. <BR>  <BR>  <p><P>Halen Sleet, 21st Barbarian Rogue, Bristlebane

