<br>
Of course I accept, and after sellign the helm and the whip I went from 1pp (long story about why not to put your D Dirk in the range slot), to 445pp.<br>
<br>
I'd say that's not half bad.<br>
<br>
Amaecyr <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub2.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=kaguelfchaser>Kagu Elfchaser</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/2/00 8:15:43 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Ohhhhh no wait till you hear this</span><hr size=1> My friends, i am a professional merchant...=]. I see a PBB for 150 pp. Pick it up. Trade that for Charred boots. Trade the charred boots and 200 pp for a staff of writhing. Trade the staff for an exe hood(i like my dwarfy pointy hat ;D), bracer of erollsi, Bi girdle, AND a stein of moggok. Then later i bought a Bi crown for 150 pp. Traded someone my hood for a charred guardian BP. (btw i have a mask of the deciever. DE's look cool with a Bi crown so now i'm inkie all the time, dwarfs dont look to hot in a Bi crown). Sold the stein for 250 pp (BTW i wanna know what server they go for 2k pp on yeesh), sold the CGBP for 1600 pp, bracer of erollsi 70 pp, and Bi girdle for 80 pp. I am a lvl 15 rogue <img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)">. So i turned 350 pp into 1750 pp. BTW this was all on brell <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.showMessage?topicID=120.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.showMessage?topicID=233.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.emailToFriend?topicID=229.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezbo